html:
Snapchat offers you control over your info & if you want to delete your account, info will also be deleted from their servers, so nothing is kept.

https://www.snapchat.com/privacy#control-over-your-information

“Account Deletion. While we hope you’ll remain a lifelong Snapchatter, if for some reason you ever want to delete your account, just go here. If you ask to delete your account, you will have up to 30 days to restore your account before we delete your information from our servers. During this period of time, your account will not be visible to other Snapchatters.”

subject: [Good] Snapchat offers you control over your info.
text:
Snapchat offers you control over your info & if you want to delete your 
account, info will also be deleted from their servers, so nothing is kept.

https://www.snapchat.com/privacy#control-over-your-information

“*Account Deletion*. While we hope you’ll remain a lifelong Snapchatter, if 
for some reason you ever want to delete your account, just go here 
<https://accounts.snapchat.com/accounts/login?continue=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.snapchat.com%2Faccounts%2Fdelete_account>. 
If you ask to delete your account, you will have up to 30 days to restore 
your account before we delete your information from our servers. During 
this period of time, your account will not be visible to other 
Snapchatters.”
